race.description: Quick Fix Appliances Country Boosted Mdn Plate
race.comment: MCTOMINAY (2) is knocking on the door. Has enough pace to offset the wide draw and should be at peak fitness now. Heywood for Pepper reads favourably. Can get the job done this time. BELNERA (6) finds the maiden win elusive but it certainly hasn't been without trying. Should settle much closer from the kinder draw this time and doesn't need to improve much to break through. CAYMAN ISLAND (4) is another that will look to roll forward from his wide draw. Has plenty of running in the legs, so should be in this for a long way. EXTRA HANDS (10) is another that finds it tough to shed the tag. Went close last time at Goulburn and gets in well with the 3kg claimer engaged, though she'll need to be switched on from her wide draw. DEFLECTOR (9) gets a key booking in McDougall and has another good chance to break through. Take on trust.
